  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>As you cast your spell, you weave in a flurry of motions or a subtle set of movements to distract a nearby target from reacting to it. Attempt a Performance check against the Perception DC of a creature you can see within 60 feet of you. On a success, you distract the enemy enough to cast your spell without incurring any reactions from them as a direct result of your spellcasting. If you’re a Master in Performance, you can affect 3 creatures. If you’re Legendary in Performance, you can affect all creatures in range.</p>"
